  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span class=3DSpellE>Rephidium</span> Ale is a delic=
ious,
  super-dry beer.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Several different variations of <span class=3DSpellE=
>Rephidium</span>
  ale are produced. Some of these blends use secret ingredients. However th=
e primary
  common ingredient is the leaves and stalks of the <span class=3DSpellE>Re=
pha</span>
  bush. <span class=3DSpellE>Rephidium</span> Ale is produced on Continental
  worlds.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Occurrence: very rare</p>
